---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Work/Life | The 4-Day Workweek Movement" active="movement">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="editorial-grid">
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container font-label text-sm font-semibold mb-6 tracking-wide">
          AN EVOLUTION OF LABOR
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-medium tracking-tight leading-[0.95] mb-8 text-on-background font-headline">
          The 4-Day <br /> <span class="italic">Workweek</span> <br /> Movement
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-on-surface-variant max-w-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          The evidence is in. Reducing work hours isn't just about time&mdash;it's about human flourishing, environmental restoration, and economic resilience.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <a href="/implementation" class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg flex items-center gap-2 hover:bg-primary-dim transition-all">
            Get Started
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/health" class="text-on-surface font-semibold text-lg flex items-center gap-2 hover:underline underline-offset-8">
            Explore the Benefits
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 relative mt-12 lg:mt-0">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative z-10 transform lg:rotate-2">
          <img alt="Collaborative office environment" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDmqdb8_mUyC0De9nKKhmabByNimleOmUJ8GNCICWwhGQOPilX9j-70UYgwKbqLqYGqiiQGe0dntk1K1JPIKNGceyMgM3cRLzvPxbY0Aprie7Jqa8ya-U2Q4OICQNJfJt6UXc7GN3bgwg6SGJzegQd81Hro96lGk0VfuX6AX_6R2ADmFoOLPSPh6W4eqELTCixayU_DicmffpmgX6Tpt2xq1WsRKx6ljzMQyEeaLL3q0SbGenXSogcTcZ30w0lP28jIPUcpEEwLLPA" />
        </div>
        <!-- Ludique Callout Element -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 bg-secondary-container p-8 rounded-xl max-w-xs z-20 shadow-xl border border-secondary-dim/10">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-secondary-dim mb-4">draw</span>
          <p class="font-body text-on-secondary-container font-medium">"We aren't just shortening the week; we're deepening the human experience of time."</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Stats Bento Grid -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- Stat 1: Productivity -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-low p-10 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between aspect-square md:aspect-auto">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-6">trending_up</span>
          <h3 class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">+40%</h3>
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-on-surface-variant">Productivity Increase</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/80">Microsoft Japan's 2019 trial saw a 39.9% productivity boost with a 4-day week.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Stat 2: Burnout -->
      <div class="bg-tertiary-container p-10 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between aspect-square md:aspect-auto">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-4xl mb-6">psychology</span>
          <h3 class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-on-tertiary-container mb-2">71%</h3>
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-on-tertiary-container/80">Burnout Reduction</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-tertiary-container/60">UK pilot participants reported 71% less burnout within six months.</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Stat 3: Environment -->
      <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between aspect-square md:aspect-auto shadow-sm ring-1 ring-on-surface/5">
        <div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-6">eco</span>
          <h3 class="text-5xl font-headline font-bold text-secondary mb-2">-21%</h3>
          <p class="text-lg font-medium text-on-surface-variant">Car Miles Reduced</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant/80">Tyler Grange reported 21% fewer car miles during their 4-day week trial.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Triple Bottom Line Section -->
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="bg-surface-container rounded-[2.5rem] p-12 lg:p-24 overflow-hidden relative">
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-medium mb-12 font-headline">The Triple Bottom Line</h2>
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">groups</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-semibold mb-2">Social Responsibility</h4>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Men spent 27% more time on childcare and 23% more on housework. The 4-day week redistributes domestic labor and strengthens communities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">forest</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-semibold mb-2">Ecological Balance</h4>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">A UK-wide shift could cut 127 million tonnes of CO2 annually. Fewer commutes, lower energy use, and reduced consumption.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-6">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center shadow-sm">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">payments</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="text-2xl font-headline font-semibold mb-2">Economic Resilience</h4>
              <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">92% of UK pilot companies continued post-trial. Turnover dropped 57%, and companies like Exos saw 211% sales pipeline growth.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Asymmetric Decorative Image -->
      <div class="absolute -right-20 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 hidden lg:block w-1/3">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl transform rotate-3 bg-surface-container-lowest p-4">
          <img alt="Natural light" class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-xl" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBbT-wunggDhxzqMcY_EsA9CJu6eJLJWoFkbmYNiYqUrvIJs2Ho9k09WKyHMuTgr9RWLiQve15Wgm7XumZFk3HabAbfVZP29ZwwiRphpLZ7Vr4PKQ3nBGIpwBXVHLCMQbFQZqJMs5Ic8SR2oKroPtnDsPS-C6Q35Rx-sSJJGnKspZQ4cHRB2Y6ZuiwVLBMT5WadK50x1TgNa6tMadCrX-k-WI4BA-vODpMLFyAR3uq-rzvW1CerWeAy18kSGvDKekwZUuIpRyG2Q8I" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Callout -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 mb-32">
    <div class="bg-secondary-container rounded-3xl p-12 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full opacity-10 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_center,_var(--tw-gradient-stops))] from-secondary to-transparent"></div>
      </div>
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl text-on-secondary-container mb-6 block">auto_awesome</span>
      <h3 class="text-4xl font-headline font-bold mb-6 text-on-secondary-container">Ready to redefine the pace of life?</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-on-secondary-container/80 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Join over 5,000 forward-thinking organizations already implementing 4-day pilots. We provide the research, the framework, and the community.
      </p>
      <a href="/implementation" class="inline-block bg-on-secondary-container text-secondary-container px-10 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
        Get Started
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
